                  div
                    p.text-ubold.text-spacing-200.text-gray-base.text-uppercase.text-small Ann Wilson
                  .offset-top-8
                    p.text-small.text-italic.text-silver-chalice “I can’t wait to share the fabulous experience. Everything was perfect! The tour was well-organized and the guide was experienced.”
